('89963','30969','5','New luxury apartment complex in 1st Sea line Portixol, Palma'),
('89964','30970','5','In the first Line to the sea of Palma de Mallorca is currently being the second construction phase, of an existing apartment complex, under construction. It’s only a 2 minute walk to the beautiful city beach of Palma. Several restaurants and chill out beach-bars are near by.\r\nThe luxury apartments have between 155m² and 325m² of living space spread over the living-dining room, kitchen, utility room, 4 bedrooms and 4 bathrooms. The master bedroom has an additional walk-in closet and access to the main terrace with sea views. One guest bedroom has a small terrace with city views. All apartments are equipped with high-quality materials such as white lacquer kitchen furniture, washer and dryer from Siemens, induction hob, large fridge, Gaggenau appliances, air conditioning hot / cold, under floor heating water / gas-solar, electric shutters, aluminum double glazed windows and much more.\r\nEach apartment has a underground parking space. A 2. can be purchased, subject to availability so. All apartments are easily accessible by elevator. \r\nThe penthouse apartments have additionally rooftop terraces with Jacuzzi and barbecue. The community offers a swimming pool, a tennis court and a children''s playground.\r\nPrices from 1.280.000€  to 2.728.000€\r\nPrices after finishing the construction:    from 1.280.000€  to  2.500.000€\r\nPayment arrangement.\r\nFor reservation contract:  payment 20% plus IVA \r\nDuring the construction phase: partial payment of 10% plus IVA \r\nAt Notary and key collection: 70% plus IVA\r\n'),
